videos.description: Frank Howard uses a nice step-back move to leave his defender stumbling before draining a 3.
videos.headline: Howard breaks defender's ankles on step-back 3

videos.description: Justin Robinson drains back-to-back 3-pointers, finishing a red hot first half where he hit seven 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Virginia Tech's Robinson can't be stopped from 3

videos.description: Oshae Brissett slides down the lane and slams it home for an easy dunk.
videos.headline: Cuse's Brissett strides down lane for dunk

videos.description: Ahmed Hill hustles down the court and throws down a two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Virginia Tech's Hill throws down fast-break dunk
